            <header class="post-header ">
                
                                            <h2 class="post-title"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/02/09/picture-of-the-day-the-power-of-the-people/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Picture of the Day:  The Power of the People">Picture of the Day:  The Power of the People</a></h2>
                <?php// rtp_hook_end_post_title(); ?>

                
            <div class="clearfix post-meta post-meta-top"><span class="author"><a class="fn" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/author/mkriegs/" title="Posts by Michael Krieger">Michael Krieger</a></span> <span class="rtp-meta-separator">|</span> Posted <time class="published" datetime="2013-02-09T17:04:29+00:00">Saturday Feb 9, 2013</time> at 5:04 pm         <span class="rtp-post-comment-count"><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/02/09/picture-of-the-day-the-power-of-the-people/#comments" class="rtp-post-comment rtp-common-link"  title="Comment on Picture of the Day:  The Power of the People"><span>3</span> Comments</a></span>
            </div><!-- .post-meta -->            </header><!-- .post-title -->

            <div class="post-content">
                                

                
                <p>The image below couldn&#8217;t be more true.  The ruling class are nothing more than a bunch of ponzi scheme running, Wizard of Oz con men.  Great job to whoever created this.</p>
<p><a href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/PeoplePower.jpg"><img class="alignnone  wp-image-3634" alt="PeoplePower" src="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/PeoplePower.jpg" width="275" height="275" /></a></p>
<p>In Liberty,<br />
Mike</p>
